{
  "number": 79,
  "title": "La oraci\u00f3n del alma es",
  "marking": "Con serenidad",
  "verses": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "lines": [
        "La oraci\u00f3n del alma es",
        "el medio de solaz",
        "que surge en el coraz\u00f3n",
        "y da eterna paz."
      ]
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "lines": [
        "La oraci\u00f3n suspiro es,",
        "y mansa humildad,",
        "de quien conf\u00eda en su Dios",
        "en horas de soledad."
      ]
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "lines": [
        "La oraci\u00f3n sencilla es",
        "de boca infantil,",
        "sublime coro en uni\u00f3n",
        "de todo el redil."
      ]
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "lines": [
        "La oraci\u00f3n la vida es",
        "para el hombre fiel.",
        "Al cielo entra al morir",
        "orando siempre \u00e9l."
      ]
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "lines": [
        "Es voz, tambi\u00e9n, del pecador",
        "que deja de pecar,",
        "y \u00e1ngeles proclamar\u00e1n:",
        "\u201cMiradle, pues, orar\u201d."
      ],
      "optional": true
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "lines": [
        "Al inclinarse en oraci\u00f3n,",
        "los santos uno son,",
        "y con el Padre y Jes\u00fas",
        "encuentran comuni\u00f3n."
      ],
      "optional": true
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "lines": [
        "No s\u00f3lo en la tierra, pues,",
        "se hace oraci\u00f3n:",
        "Jes\u00fas suplica ante Dios,",
        "busc\u00e1ndonos perd\u00f3n."
      ],
      "optional": true
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "lines": [
        "La senda de la oraci\u00f3n",
        "has recorrido ya;",
        "oh Cristo, nuestro Salvador,",
        "ens\u00e9\u00f1anos a orar."
      ],
      "optional": true
    }
  ],
  "credits": [
